Int. Saylor’s Temporary House - Fireplace Room

11 PM.  SAYLOR and RICK, nearly a yard/meter apart, sit by a blazing live fire in the fireplace, sunk into their big soft armchairs.  They’re checking the channel’s performance: SAYLOR on her tablet and RICK on his phone.

RICK
Oh look, the video we dropped 2 weeks ago has garnered 307 thousands views, that’s a hit.

SAYLOR
Reached top-5 on the channel, huh, that’s stellar!

RICK
Ha-hey!

SAYLOR and RICK high-five.

RICK
So there’s still enough monetization to keep the wheels turning.

SAYLOR
